    "description": "Merck India Ventures Solutions has an exciting opening for a Senior Doctor at our Nagpur office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Merck India Ventures Solutions:\nMerck India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Merck India Ventures Solutions!",
